==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Devulgarize
<hw>De*vul"gar*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To free from
what is vulgar, common, or narrow.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Shakespeare and Plutarch's ⟦ldquo⟧Lives⟦rdquo⟧ are very
<qex>devulgarizing</qex> books.</q> <rj><qau>E. A.
Abbott.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dew</ent>⟦br⟧
